{"surah":{"number":79,"name":"النازعات","englishName":"An-Nazi'at","englishTranslation":"Those who drag forth","ayahCount":46},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:38.806Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"By those [angels] who extract with violence","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلنَّـٰزِعَـٰتِ","english":"By those who extract","translit":"wal-nāziʿāti","root":"نزع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"غَرْقًۭا","english":"violently","translit":"gharqan","root":"غرق"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"And [by] those who remove with ease","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلنَّـٰشِطَـٰتِ","english":"And those who draw out","translit":"wal-nāshiṭāti","root":"نشط"},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَشْطًۭا","english":"gently","translit":"nashṭan","root":"نشط"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"And [by] those who glide [as if] swimming","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلسَّـٰبِحَـٰتِ","english":"And those who glide","translit":"wal-sābiḥāti","root":"سبح"},{"position":2,"arabic":"سَبْحًۭا","english":"swimming","translit":"sabḥan","root":"سبح"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"And those who race each other in a race","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱلسَّـٰبِقَـٰتِ","english":"And those who race each other","translit":"fal-sābiqāti","root":"سبق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"سَبْقًۭا","english":"(in) a race","translit":"sabqan","root":"سبق"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"And those who arrange [each] matter,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱلْمُدَبِّرَٰتِ","english":"And those who arrange","translit":"fal-mudabirāti","root":"دبر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَمْرًۭا","english":"(the) matter","translit":"amran","root":"أمر"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"On the Day the blast [of the Horn] will convulse [creation],","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَرْجُفُ","english":"will quake","translit":"tarjufu","root":"رجف"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلرَّاجِفَةُ","english":"the quaking one","translit":"l-rājifatu","root":"رجف"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"There will follow it the subsequent [one].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"تَتْبَعُهَا","english":"Follows it","translit":"tatbaʿuhā","root":"تبع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلرَّادِفَةُ","english":"the subsequent","translit":"l-rādifatu","root":"ردف"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"Hearts, that Day, will tremble,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قُلُوبٌۭ","english":"Hearts","translit":"qulūbun","root":"قلب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"that Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَاجِفَةٌ","english":"will palpitate","translit":"wājifatun","root":"وجف"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"Their eyes humbled.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَبْصَـٰرُهَا","english":"Their eyes","translit":"abṣāruhā","root":"بصر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"خَـٰشِعَةٌۭ","english":"humbled","translit":"khāshiʿatun","root":"خشع"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"They are [presently] saying, \"Will we indeed be returned to [our] former state [of life]?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَقُولُونَ","english":"They say","translit":"yaqūlūna","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَءِنَّا","english":"Will we","translit":"a-innā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَمَرْدُودُونَ","english":"indeed be returned","translit":"lamardūdūna","root":"ردد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فِى","english":"to","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْحَافِرَةِ","english":"the former state","translit":"l-ḥāfirati","root":"حفر"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"Even if we should be decayed bones?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَءِذَا","english":"What! When","translit":"a-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كُنَّا","english":"we are","translit":"kunnā","root":"كون"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عِظَـٰمًۭا","english":"bones","translit":"ʿiẓāman","root":"عظم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"نَّخِرَةًۭ","english":"decayed","translit":"nakhiratan","root":"نخر"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"They say, \"That, then, would be a losing return.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","english":"They say","translit":"qālū","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"تِلْكَ","english":"This","translit":"til'ka","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِذًۭا","english":"then","translit":"idhan","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"كَرَّةٌ","english":"(would be) a return","translit":"karratun","root":"كرر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"خَاسِرَةٌۭ","english":"losing","translit":"khāsiratun","root":"خسر"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"Indeed, it will be but one shout,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِنَّمَا","english":"Then only","translit":"fa-innamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هِىَ","english":"it","translit":"hiya","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"زَجْرَةٌۭ","english":"(will be) a shout","translit":"zajratun","root":"زجر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَٰحِدَةٌۭ","english":"single","translit":"wāḥidatun","root":"وحد"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"And suddenly they will be [alert] upon the earth's surface.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِذَا","english":"And behold","translit":"fa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُم","english":"They","translit":"hum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِٱلسَّاهِرَةِ","english":"(will be) awakened","translit":"bil-sāhirati","root":"سهر"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"Has there reached you the story of Moses? -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"هَلْ","english":"Has","translit":"hal","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَتَىٰكَ","english":"(there) come to you","translit":"atāka","root":"أتي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"حَدِيثُ","english":"(the) story","translit":"ḥadīthu","root":"حدث"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مُوسَىٰٓ","english":"(of) Musa","translit":"mūsā","root":""}]},{"number":16,"translation":"When his Lord called to him in the sacred valley of Tuwa,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِذْ","english":"When","translit":"idh","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَادَىٰهُ","english":"called him","translit":"nādāhu","root":"ندي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبُّهُۥ","english":"his Lord","translit":"rabbuhu","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِٱلْوَادِ","english":"in the valley","translit":"bil-wādi","root":"ودي"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْمُقَدَّسِ","english":"the sacred","translit":"l-muqadasi","root":"قدس"},{"position":6,"arabic":"طُوًى","english":"(of) Tuwa","translit":"ṭuwan","root":"طوي"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"\"Go to Pharaoh. Indeed, he has transgressed.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱذْهَبْ","english":"Go","translit":"idh'hab","root":"ذهب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِرْعَوْنَ","english":"Firaun","translit":"fir'ʿawna","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","english":"Indeed, he","translit":"innahu","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"طَغَىٰ","english":"(has) transgressed","translit":"ṭaghā","root":"طغي"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"And say to him, 'Would you [be willing to] purify yourself","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَقُلْ","english":"And say","translit":"faqul","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"هَل","english":"Would","translit":"hal","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَّكَ","english":"[for] you","translit":"laka","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِلَىٰٓ","english":"[to]","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَن","english":"[that]","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"تَزَكَّىٰ","english":"purify yourself","translit":"tazakkā","root":"زكو"}]},{"number":19,"translation":"And let me guide you to your Lord so you would fear [Him]?'\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَهْدِيَكَ","english":"And I will guide you","translit":"wa-ahdiyaka","root":"هدي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ","english":"your Lord","translit":"rabbika","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَتَخْشَىٰ","english":"so you would fear","translit":"fatakhshā","root":"خشي"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"And he showed him the greatest sign,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَرَىٰهُ","english":"Then he showed him","translit":"fa-arāhu","root":"رأي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْـَٔايَةَ","english":"the sign","translit":"l-āyata","root":"أيي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْكُبْرَىٰ","english":"the great","translit":"l-kub'rā","root":"كبر"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"But Pharaoh denied and disobeyed.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَكَذَّبَ","english":"But he denied","translit":"fakadhaba","root":"كذب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَعَصَىٰ","english":"and disobeyed","translit":"waʿaṣā","root":"عصي"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"Then he turned his back, striving.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"Then","translit":"thumma","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَدْبَرَ","english":"he turned his back","translit":"adbara","root":"دبر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَسْعَىٰ","english":"striving","translit":"yasʿā","root":"سعي"}]},{"number":23,"translation":"And he gathered [his people] and called out","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَحَشَرَ","english":"And he gathered","translit":"faḥashara","root":"حشر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فَنَادَىٰ","english":"and called out","translit":"fanādā","root":"ندي"}]},{"number":24,"translation":"And said, \"I am your most exalted lord.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَقَالَ","english":"Then he said","translit":"faqāla","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَنَا۠","english":"I am","translit":"anā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبُّكُمُ","english":"your Lord","translit":"rabbukumu","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْأَعْلَىٰ","english":"the Most High","translit":"l-aʿlā","root":"علو"}]},{"number":25,"translation":"So Allah seized him in exemplary punishment for the last and the first [transgression].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَخَذَهُ","english":"So seized him","translit":"fa-akhadhahu","root":"أخذ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":3,"arabic":"نَكَالَ","english":"(with) an exemplary punishment","translit":"nakāla","root":"نكل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْـَٔاخِرَةِ","english":"(for) the last","translit":"l-ākhirati","root":"أخر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْأُولَىٰٓ","english":"and the first","translit":"wal-ūlā","root":"أول"}]},{"number":26,"translation":"Indeed in that is a warning for whoever would fear [Allah].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"that","translit":"dhālika","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَعِبْرَةًۭ","english":"surely (is) a lesson","translit":"laʿib'ratan","root":"عبر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لِّمَن","english":"for whoever","translit":"liman","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"يَخْشَىٰٓ","english":"fears","translit":"yakhshā","root":"خشي"}]},{"number":27,"translation":"Are you a more difficult creation or is the heaven? Allah constructed it.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ءَأَنتُمْ","english":"Are you","translit":"a-antum","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَشَدُّ","english":"a more difficult","translit":"ashaddu","root":"شدد"},{"position":3,"arabic":"خَلْقًا","english":"creation","translit":"khalqan","root":"خلق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَمِ","english":"or","translit":"ami","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءُ ۚ","english":"the heaven","translit":"l-samāu","root":"سمو"},{"position":6,"arabic":"بَنَىٰهَا","english":"He constructed it","translit":"banāhā","root":"بني","audio":"wbw/079_027_007.mp3"}]},{"number":28,"translation":"He raised its ceiling and proportioned it.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"رَفَعَ","english":"He raised","translit":"rafaʿa","root":"رفع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"سَمْكَهَا","english":"its ceiling","translit":"samkahā","root":"سمك"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَسَوَّىٰهَا","english":"and proportioned it","translit":"fasawwāhā","root":"سوي"}]},{"number":29,"translation":"And He darkened its night and extracted its brightness.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَغْطَشَ","english":"And He darkened","translit":"wa-aghṭasha","root":"غطش"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَيْلَهَا","english":"its night","translit":"laylahā","root":"ليل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَأَخْرَجَ","english":"and brought out","translit":"wa-akhraja","root":"خرج"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ضُحَىٰهَا","english":"its brightness","translit":"ḍuḥāhā","root":"ضحو"}]},{"number":30,"translation":"And after that He spread the earth.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضَ","english":"And the earth","translit":"wal-arḍa","root":"أرض"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بَعْدَ","english":"after","translit":"baʿda","root":"بعد"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"that","translit":"dhālika","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"دَحَىٰهَآ","english":"He spread it","translit":"daḥāhā","root":"دحو"}]},{"number":31,"translation":"He extracted from it its water and its pasture,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَخْرَجَ","english":"He brought forth","translit":"akhraja","root":"خرج"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِنْهَا","english":"from it","translit":"min'hā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَآءَهَا","english":"its water","translit":"māahā","root":"موه"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَمَرْعَىٰهَا","english":"and its pasture","translit":"wamarʿāhā","root":"رعي"}]},{"number":32,"translation":"And the mountains He set firmly","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلْجِبَالَ","english":"And the mountains","translit":"wal-jibāla","root":"جبل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَرْسَىٰهَا","english":"He made them firm","translit":"arsāhā","root":"رسو"}]},{"number":33,"translation":"As provision for you and your grazing livestock.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مَتَـٰعًۭا","english":"(As) a provision","translit":"matāʿan","root":"متع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَّكُمْ","english":"for you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَلِأَنْعَـٰمِكُمْ","english":"and for your cattle","translit":"wali-anʿāmikum","root":"نعم"}]},{"number":34,"translation":"But when there comes the greatest Overwhelming Calamity -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِذَا","english":"But when","translit":"fa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"جَآءَتِ","english":"comes","translit":"jāati","root":"جيأ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلطَّآمَّةُ","english":"the Overwhelming Calamity","translit":"l-ṭāmatu","root":"طمم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْكُبْرَىٰ","english":"the great","translit":"l-kub'rā","root":"كبر"}]},{"number":35,"translation":"The Day when man will remember that for which he strove,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَتَذَكَّرُ","english":"will remember","translit":"yatadhakkaru","root":"ذكر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ","english":"man","translit":"l-insānu","root":"أنس"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"سَعَىٰ","english":"he strove (for)","translit":"saʿā","root":"سعي"}]},{"number":36,"translation":"And Hellfire will be exposed for [all] those who see -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَبُرِّزَتِ","english":"And will be made manifest","translit":"waburrizati","root":"برز"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجَحِيمُ","english":"the Hellfire","translit":"l-jaḥīmu","root":"جحم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِمَن","english":"to (him) who","translit":"liman","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَرَىٰ","english":"sees","translit":"yarā","root":"رأي"}]},{"number":37,"translation":"So as for he who transgressed","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَمَّا","english":"Then as for","translit":"fa-ammā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَن","english":"(him) who","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"طَغَىٰ","english":"transgressed","translit":"ṭaghā","root":"طغي"}]},{"number":38,"translation":"And preferred the life of the world,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَءَاثَرَ","english":"And preferred","translit":"waāthara","root":"أثر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْحَيَوٰةَ","english":"the life","translit":"l-ḥayata","root":"حيي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلدُّنْيَا","english":"(of) the world","translit":"l-dun'yā","root":"دنو"}]},{"number":39,"translation":"Then indeed, Hellfire will be [his] refuge.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِنَّ","english":"Then indeed","translit":"fa-inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجَحِيمَ","english":"the Hellfire","translit":"l-jaḥīma","root":"جحم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"هِىَ","english":"it","translit":"hiya","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمَأْوَىٰ","english":"(is) the refuge","translit":"l-mawā","root":"أوي"}]},{"number":40,"translation":"But as for he who feared the position of his Lord and prevented the soul from [unlawful] inclination,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَمَّا","english":"But as for","translit":"wa-ammā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَنْ","english":"(him) who","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"خَافَ","english":"feared","translit":"khāfa","root":"خوف"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَقَامَ","english":"standing","translit":"maqāma","root":"قوم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"رَبِّهِۦ","english":"(before) his Lord","translit":"rabbihi","root":"ربب"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَنَهَى","english":"and restrained","translit":"wanahā","root":"نهي"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلنَّفْسَ","english":"his soul","translit":"l-nafsa","root":"نفس"},{"position":8,"arabic":"عَنِ","english":"from","translit":"ʿani","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْهَوَىٰ","english":"the vain desires","translit":"l-hawā","root":"هوي"}]},{"number":41,"translation":"Then indeed, Paradise will be [his] refuge.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِنَّ","english":"Then indeed","translit":"fa-inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجَنَّةَ","english":"Paradise","translit":"l-janata","root":"جنن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"هِىَ","english":"it (is)","translit":"hiya","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمَأْوَىٰ","english":"the refuge","translit":"l-mawā","root":"أوي"}]},{"number":42,"translation":"They ask you, [O Muhammad], about the Hour: when is its arrival?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَسْـَٔلُونَكَ","english":"They ask you","translit":"yasalūnaka","root":"سأل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَنِ","english":"about","translit":"ʿani","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلسَّاعَةِ","english":"the Hour","translit":"l-sāʿati","root":"سوع"},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَيَّانَ","english":"when","translit":"ayyāna","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"مُرْسَىٰهَا","english":"(is) its arrival","translit":"mur'sāhā","root":"رسو"}]},{"number":43,"translation":"In what [position] are you that you should mention it?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فِيمَ","english":"In what","translit":"fīma","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَنتَ","english":"(are) you","translit":"anta","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِن","english":"[of]","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ذِكْرَىٰهَآ","english":"(to) mention it","translit":"dhik'rāhā","root":"ذكر"}]},{"number":44,"translation":"To your Lord is its finality.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"To","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ","english":"your Lord","translit":"rabbika","root":"ربب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مُنتَهَىٰهَآ","english":"(is) its finality","translit":"muntahāhā","root":"نهي"}]},{"number":45,"translation":"You are only a warner for those who fear it.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّمَآ","english":"Only","translit":"innamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَنتَ","english":"you","translit":"anta","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"مُنذِرُ","english":"(are) a warner","translit":"mundhiru","root":"نذر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَن","english":"(for him) who","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَخْشَىٰهَا","english":"fears it","translit":"yakhshāhā","root":"خشي"}]},{"number":46,"translation":"It will be, on the Day they see it, as though they had not remained [in the world] except for an afternoon or a morning thereof.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمْ","english":"As though they","translit":"ka-annahum","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(the) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَرَوْنَهَا","english":"they see it","translit":"yarawnahā","root":"رأي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَمْ","english":"not","translit":"lam","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَلْبَثُوٓا۟","english":"they had remained","translit":"yalbathū","root":"لبث"},{"position":6,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"عَشِيَّةً","english":"an evening","translit":"ʿashiyyatan","root":"عشو"},{"position":8,"arabic":"أَوْ","english":"or","translit":"aw","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"ضُحَىٰهَا","english":"a morning thereof","translit":"ḍuḥāhā","root":"ضحو"}]}]}
